  "text": "#include <stdio.h>\n\nstruct Point {\n    int x;\n    int y;\n};\n\nint add(int a, int b) {\n    return a + b;\n}\n\nvoid print_point(struct Point p) {\n    printf(\"(%d, %d)\\n\", p.x, p.y);\n}\n\nint main() {\n    struct Point p = {3, 4};\n    print_point(p);\n    return 0;\n}\n",
